Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Free movie passes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:05.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc gave them to Haibara-{\i1}san{\i0} so we could all go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:08.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can see whatever movie we want...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great? Let's all go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! This Wednesday, the anniversary of the school's opening,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will be the Detective Boys' movie watching meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:21.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should call it a film appreciation club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:23.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come too, won't you, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, nah, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:29.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you, Conan?! Ain't you planning to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:34.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After Haibara-{\i1}san{\i0} got these tickets just for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just won them in a drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:45.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to strengthen the Detective Boys' bonds of friendship, we go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:47.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right! To strengthen the bonds of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And how will we strengthen the bonds of friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine, I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason I can't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Guess I'll have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The great detective loses face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomera! Gomera!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely Gomera!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:12.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I thought we were the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:18.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we watch something like "The Onimaru Legend Murder Mystery" at the Kaminari Theatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to think to watch that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:25.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the perfect day for a popcorn movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:28.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to see, Haibara-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:35.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How does "Einstein's Days of Glory and Anguish" sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Einstein?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Is it tasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Now {\i1}that{\i0} sounds like a boring movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:47.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it—let's just split up and watch what we want. That's simple enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:53.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When Doc gave Haibara-{\i1}san{\i0} these tickets, he told us to see a movie together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:04:00.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this, there's only one choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No other way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper, rock, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.89,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No! What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.81,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I should never have publicized the results of my research!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:19.15,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Thanks to my discoveries, millions of innocents will perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.57,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Has humanity no hope left...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:26.16,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}...but to rely on a mere legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:30.62,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The legendary monster Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Gomera!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the cannibals defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose, Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for the head! That's the weak spot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:57.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With three out of five bucking for Gomera, I guess I didn't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:01.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, this flick is pretty well made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:05.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The doom of fools who put their faith in science...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exciting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you kids! Quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't stand up and wave your arms around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:21.13,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(314,334)}Toshiyuki Ide\NUniversity Student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people are trying to watch the movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be considerate of the rest of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does he think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:32.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys {\i1}were{\i0} being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The theatre's almost empty anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:40.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apart from us, there are only four other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:44.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our school's the only one that has today off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the anniversary of our founding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is a really old movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:52.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad told me not to come to this theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said there's been a lot of brawls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my mom told me that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:06:01.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This theatre sure is messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I see stepladders lying around...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:07.38,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and ropes and wires on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Maybe they're renovating the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomera's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:28.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was so little in this movie,\Nand his face was weird and scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:35.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first movie in the Gomera series. It was made before we were born!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you think, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:46.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I saw that movie a million times when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:49.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go play soccer or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about, Conan?\NWe've still got two to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:59.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A triple feature? And I've seen them all before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:03.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All told, a luxurious six hours. Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I want some snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got popcorn at the concession stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing we came, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haibara-{\i1}san{\i0}! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:20.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two more after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not exactly torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:31.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you just need to rest your neurons and take a little vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vacation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:41.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep using your head all the time, you'll go bald like Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! Three colas and two iced coffees!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And five tubs of popcorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... We only ordered three popcorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:53.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm throwing them in free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:59.83,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(294,338)}Yuriko Tomosato (23)\NConcession Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:57.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you kids around all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're our last audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As of tomorrow, we're shutting down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After 30 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.71,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(326,338)}Akio Muramatsu (62)\NMovie Theatre Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this theatre's closing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:14.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's why there's rope and stuff scattered around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:19.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The workers are already getting ready to dismantle the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:22.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those creeps! Couldn't they wait until tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. Such harsh words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:29.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tear this place down as soon as I could,\Nbut I've kindly given you this extra day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:35.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, your owner here begged me to wait until the anniversary of the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:37.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Haruta-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:42.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped by to witness the final\Nhurrah for your little movie shack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:43.66,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,300)\pos(332,300)}Seiji Haruta (42)\NReal Estate Agent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's not much of a turnout, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:52.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Gomera could stomp on this place.\NIt'd save me a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No smoking in the theatre!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:57.51,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(304,334)}Minoru Furuhashi (39)\NProjectionist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, I'll be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:09.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, this place won't be here starting tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "How many times"—does that mean that guy comes here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Lately, it's every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:28.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And whenever he's here, a couple of thugs\Nalways start a fight in the middle of a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be he hired those thugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:35.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He made them cause trouble to\Ndrive the theatre out of business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come now. How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the guy from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Ide-{\i1}kun{\i0}. Is he here again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:54.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. He wanted to take\Na few photos on the last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid's a big fan of monster movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:02.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been coming here since he was a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's almost like a son to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:09.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, time for lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! I forgot to pick up lunch for the staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go get the lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We agreed you'd stay here\Nand enjoy the monster movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:21.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Yuri-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go buy them while I start the next movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not much chance of a sellout crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:33.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And if anybody comes in, the lady at\Nthe ticket counter will take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:37.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! Almost time to start the first reel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:40.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and we're out of tea leaves!\NCan you pick some up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but we'll never use up a whole box now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're closing this place down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:52.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And they ran so many great movies here, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:10.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So now that thing's going to lay eggs inside Gomera...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:31.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I bet that rumor about the hired thugs is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That poor old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I haven't seen the Gomera movies in years. Might as well enjoy 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're scared, Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think the air's cranked up a little high?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.34,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's been that way for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:31.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I guess not even monster movies can keep a little kid awake forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:34.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haibara. Ayumi's fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you change seats with me so I can go to the bath—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:40.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't tell me I'm stuck here until the movie's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}And the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:48.91,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Gomera...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.37,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Gomera, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.16,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\blur2}Please calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Emera the fairy is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:54.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.79,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Furuhashi-{\i1}san{\i0}! I've made you a cup of tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've left it right there for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.01,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.10,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:13.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a shadow on the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Something's hanging in front of the projector!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Go downstairs and take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:23.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:26.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:35.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you never get a chance to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The deceased is Seiji Haruta-{\i1}san{\i0}, age 43.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He owns a real estate company nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:56.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He recently bought this theatre,\Nwhich was going to close tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Haruta-{\i1}san{\i0} come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Almost every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:09.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But not for the movies—just to see how the demolition was coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nothing but a thug!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:15.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what his problem was,\Nbut he was always ticked off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he was obstructing our business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:21.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He smoked in the theatre, no matter how many times we told him not to,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he heckled the audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:27.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and to top it off, he always sat in the very back row, right in front of the projector!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:31.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The smoke from his cigarettes blocked the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a huge pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:36.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've been smoking again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:39.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed some shadows on\Nthe screen every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:44.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it true? Did he hang himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:49.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And right in front of the projector, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:54.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,casting his shadow right onto the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when Emera was on screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:05.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The scene where Emera is\Ntrying to calm Gomera down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:09.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw a huge swaying shadow appear\Nwhile Emera's face was on the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh geez, you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:17.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That scene is a little before the midpoint of the movie, so it must have been around...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:19.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,12:44.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:25.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the movie started on schedule,\Nit would've been at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ide-{\i1}kun{\i0} is a huge fan of monster movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}. Did you find anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:45.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the ticket lady, there were only those four in the theatre other than the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:54.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After the movie started, she was chatting with a friend from the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:57.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:04.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So only you four of you could have killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:09.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Inspector! It was a suicide, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:15.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how could an old man, a teenage girl or a little weedy guy hang a big thug like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:21.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I could've done it,\Nbut I was in the projection room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:22.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yuri-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:23.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:29.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow appeared just as I was giving\NFuruhashi-{\i1}san{\i0} his lunch and a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:30.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And where were you two at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the theatre, watching the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you could've done it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know each other pretty well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid you're way off base.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I have an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A digital camera, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:53.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A photograph of the death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was sheer luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:02.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get a shot of the theatre with\None of my favorite scenes on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you could have taken this photo after you hanged him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check the rest of the photos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:12.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I took lots of pictures during the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:16.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's obvious I was in my seat the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a digital camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:23.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The photos could have been taken in\Nadvance and altered on a computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:26.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see Mitsuhiko and the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:36.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is when Mitsuhiko came back from the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:42.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And look at the picture with the shadow in it, five shots later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right there in the seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See, he couldn't have created these photos in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't know we'd be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:01.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Muramatsu, why did you leave your seat in the middle of the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:05.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't look like you were headed for the lavatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to check the cooling system.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The cooling system?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was set a little too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought it was too cold in there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was why I got up and went to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:24.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the controls for the cooling system?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:29.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Through the door to the right of the screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:34.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There, at the end of the corridor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:38.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my job to set the thermostat on the cooling system,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but for some reason it was set a lot higher today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:44.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The cooling system's not important, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:47.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The important thing is whether this is a murder or suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:54.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you mind showing me the projection room?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:58.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the stairs that lead in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:01.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no customers allowed past this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the projector?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The projectors are over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:13.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:19.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I use one to project the movie and the other to rewind the previous reel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it with just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a long time to rewind a reel,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we wouldn't be able to start the next showing on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:32.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the observation window, where I check to make sure the film is projected properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is the window through which the film is projected.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:41.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the window the guy hanged himself in front of!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This window doesn't open, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:46.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's sealed shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the shadow appeared, I was right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:53.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-{\i1}chan{\i0} was in the room next door, making me some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Airtight alibi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it was just a suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just come up with a neat idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:03.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Neat idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:08.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could split the reel into two halves at Emera's scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and use that projector to play the first half,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:14.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then switch to this projector to play the second half!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:19.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Then the body wouldn't interfere with the first half of the movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:21.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and would cast a shadow on the screen the moment it changed to the second half!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:26.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the body could have been hung there beforehand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you think, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a smart idea, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And some movie theatres really do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:39.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you cut a reel, it leaves an obvious mark when you reconnect the films.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:43.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, feel free to check the reel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you'll find nothing like that around that scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:52.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I got a glimpse of this room when I brought lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:56.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the only moving projector was the one by the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:57.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:00.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you come back with the lunches?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:05.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About five minutes before that shadow appeared and everybody freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was around 12:40 or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:13.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could all eat together at the next intermission,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I went to a convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:19.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I got back, I asked the ticket lady for the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask her yourself, if you want to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:28.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, you were in this room until you heard the commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:33.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to make me some tea, so you were boiling water, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:35.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stove's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This room's so messy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:42.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They should at least get a new mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:46.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding. It's dusty and the ash tray is filled with cigarette butts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you clean the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:52.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off! Tomorrow they're going to tear everything down anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:57.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we'll need to borrow that reel, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:58.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, do what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:08.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:11.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:14.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you see, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:16.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:22.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That lady was in the girls' room, looking in the mirror and rubbing her eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:24.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(136,98)\b1\fnSegoe\fscx105\fs28\fsp1\shad0\bord0\alpha&H1F&}NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:06.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You strive to hunt for the truth,\Nbut you're forced to deceive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:14.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even the perfect reflection\Nof this mirror shows our true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:18.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Haibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:19.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:22.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's it! That's what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:23.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's why that scene...
